    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款关于猫咪营救主人的2D平台解密冒险游戏</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中，猫猫的主人因车祸惨遭不幸，你将扮演一只叫“未来”的猫咪，通过灵活运用自己九条命“<strong>死而复生</strong>”的能力，穿越冥界的重重阻碍，最后用自己的能力复活主人</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这里，你可以欣赏到<strong><u>唯美精致的画面</u></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108050/extras/6ba8edac04dc3149a7c5b08999b6f20f.poster.avif?t=1736013527\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108050/extras/6ba8edac04dc3149a7c5b08999b6f20f.webm?t=1736013527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108050/extras/6ba8edac04dc3149a7c5b08999b6f20f.mp4?t=1736013527\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>一段扣人心弦的故事</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108050/extras/c93b9b090d64e3972e988e32d582cd1d.poster.avif?t=1736013527\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108050/extras/c93b9b090d64e3972e988e32d582cd1d.webm?t=1736013527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108050/extras/c93b9b090d64e3972e988e32d582cd1d.mp4?t=1736013527\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>一道道充满挑战的关卡</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108050/extras/32efbd236ef5de97cda91af55fccde92.poster.avif?t=1736013527\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108050/extras/32efbd236ef5de97cda91af55fccde92.webm?t=1736013527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108050/extras/32efbd236ef5de97cda91af55fccde92.mp4?t=1736013527\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>一场与时间的赛跑</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108050/extras/ebc61d672c133e5ac84763fb07b94185.poster.avif?t=1736013527\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108050/extras/ebc61d672c133e5ac84763fb07b94185.webm?t=1736013527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108050/extras/ebc61d672c133e5ac84763fb07b94185.mp4?t=1736013527\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除此之外，游戏内还有着双结局的结局选项<i>（<span class=\"bb_strike\">在这里就不给大家剧透了）</span></i>，话不多说，赶紧来下载体验吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>游戏为2024CIGA gamejam参赛作品，制作团队平均年龄只有18岁，主制作人目前就读高中，制作有不足的地方请见谅！有建议可以在评论区提出~</i></strong></p>",
